{"tid":2393306,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年承認破壞「喜茶」 官拒索感化報告免給予假希望 明言受制於上訴庭","createTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T15:11:16.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"76978b179260f03b25be7e73ce3186b308023125","tid":2393306,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"網民去年5月號召到各區商場「和你Sing」，當日沙田新城市廣場「喜茶」店舖內設施遭人破壞，警方事後拘捕6名中學生。其中一名被告早前承認刑事毀壞罪，被判社會服務令。另一名被告今亦承認刑事毀壞及拒捕罪，<span class=\"red\">署理主任裁判官溫紹明聽罷求情後無奈表示，自本案首名被告的判刑後，上級法院頒下多宗案例，對本案有約束力，不欲給予被告假希望</span>，故先索取更生中心、教導所及勞教中心報告，還押至本月17日判刑，並須向「喜茶」賠償3,800元。<br />\n<br />\n警方檢查另一被告的手機，發現有人於案發前18分鐘在WhatsApp開設名為「heycondom」群組，兩名被告均為群組成員。兩被告於群組內提供逃走路線，又被要求按指示衝入店舖內破壞。警方亦發現另一個群組，周曾於組內建議成員案發當日帶備工具。"},{"pid":"2cc9cd6f164aaf24d8502a10b6d05b3adadb9164","tid":2393306,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:04:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/ZENBZM22EZAMBIE45M47C6CHU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FZENBZM22EZAMBIE45M47C6CHU4%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdje8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=715ac4e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FZENBZM22EZAMBIE45M47C6CHU4%2F&h=b8b1982c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/ZENBZM22EZAMBIE45M47C6CHU4/</a>"},{"pid":"f77097aad0c75ba95261f2b12c60f5fd73c097e0","tid":2393306,"uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"佢都無撚晒計"},{"pid":"7bf6b4a9c63642fc3bba6f309074de6ed90e5d84","tid":2393306,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf390f48a28e650cf16